Bausch and Lomb Inc said itsboard of directors has authorized the repurchase of up to threemln of its 30.5 mln issued shares of common stock.    The company said recent turmoil in the financial marketshas resulted in its stock being priced substantially below alevel which it believes to be an accurate reflection of thecompany's present performance and future earnings potential.    The shares will be repurchased at management's discretion,either in the open market, or by private purchase, and will beused in connection with acquisitions, stock options andemployee benefit plans. Reuter&#3;